					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8534490#post-4060667</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8534490/scp-3495#post-4060667</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 17 Nov 2018 03:36:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>JayrassicPark</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2924850</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm liking the weird twisting of Mormon myth, Nostadamus-style imagery, and post-Torah Abrahamic&#8230; stuff. I'll go in depth when I'm not suffering from a massive forest fire choking out the Bay Area, but for now:</p> <p>Sticking this longpost under spoilers.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>June 6th, 1916 - either <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/June_1916#June_6,_1916_(Tuesday)">a massive outbreak of storms in the US, or tunnel warfare in WW1.</a></p> <p>December 17th, 1936 - <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pope_Francis">Pope Francis is born.</a></p> <p>June 10th, 1957 - <a href="https://books.google.com/books?id=Nz8EAAAAMBAJ&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;source=gbs_ge_summary_r&amp;cad=0#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false">shot in the dark, but I'm wondering if it has to do with the nuclear tensions of the time.</a></p> <p>December 25th, 1960 - I got nothing, I keep thinking 'malachite' refers to something Mormon&#8230; besides being a rock.</p> <p>May 5th, 1968 - <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/May_1968#May_5,_1968_(Sunday)">May Offensive in Vietnam?</a> My initial kneejerk reaction was 'the anthrax killing sheep' incident, but that's off.</p> <p>October 3rd, 1970 - Should be obvious. :V</p> <p>I'm also going to guess the portal in the manger being destroyed was either ORIA, Horizon, or Manna&#8230; or Israel destroying it.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
