				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8534490#post-4055738</guid>
				<title>This Author Commentary Doesn&#039;t Monkey Around</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8534490/scp-3495#post-4055738</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 11 Nov 2018 06:24:42 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ihp</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1267048</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>You try coming up with non-cliche monkey jokes. :^V</p> <p>This was (re)written as part of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542099414" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" >Rimple</a></span>'s DraftSwap, original draft belongs to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meserach" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1507289&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542099414" alt="Meserach" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1507289)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meserach" >Meserach</a></span>. My biggest concern with this is the fact that literally <em>nobody</em> knows who St. Brendan is; I know Catholic saints can be obscure, but this guy is the patron saint of <em>Travelers</em>. There's a Wikipedia page about him, and a translation of the original <em>Voyage of St. Brendan</em> is allegedly available online, but it's filled with garbage text because the people who digitized it thought it would be a good idea to let an AI read it after they scanned it.</p> <p>Rant aside, thank you to everyone who critted, including <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meserach" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1507289&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542099414" alt="Meserach" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1507289)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meserach" >Meserach</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542099414" alt="UraniumEmpire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" >UraniumEmpire</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542099414" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542099414" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" >not_a_seagull</a></span>, and Azmoeth1.</p> 
